{"TopicId":97274,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Signature Picture Dimensions?","CreatedByName":"Engineer of Stuff","CreatedById":106757,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-20T16:08:08Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Engineer of Stuff","CreatedById":106757,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-20T16:08:08Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWhat is the dimensions of a signature picture?\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThanks!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Commander Jebidiah","CreatedById":78685,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-20T16:31:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E750 x 120 or 200.00kB wh8chever is smaller\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starwhip","CreatedById":83990,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-21T01:12:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E750 x 120? What? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_shocked.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:0.0:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EThat\u0027s a weird shape.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-21T01:13:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EMakes a wide but low banner strip \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starwhip","CreatedById":83990,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-21T01:17:07Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWhy not make it 750 x 750 and call it a day? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-21T01:17:19Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EAlso keeps people from posting 1024x768 animated gifs of their rockets exploding.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Starwhip\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Starwhip\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EWhy not make it 750 x 750 and call it a day? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003EBecause 750 is WAY too tall for a signature. Signatures - once you see them - are noise. Posts are signal. The signal should always drown out the noise.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Starwhip","CreatedById":83990,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-01-21T01:18:42Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EWait.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EI thought he said \u003Cem\u003Eavatar\u003C/em\u003E images.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EStop doing that, brain!\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}